'''布拉德·古赞'''（{{lang-en|'''Brad Guzan'''}}，{{bd|1984年|9月9日|catidx=Guzan, Brad}}）是一名[[美國|美國]]職業足球員，擔任[[守門員|守門員]]，現時效力[[美國職業足球大聯盟|美國職業足球大聯盟]]球會[[阿特蘭大聯足球會|阿特蘭大聯]]。

==生平==
2008年8月1日，[[英超|英超]]球會[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]替古辛辦妥工作證後，完成其從[[美職聯|美職聯]]球會[[美国芝华士|美国芝华士]]轉會程序，轉會費金額據報為200萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/7503296.stm |title=Villa-bound Guzan granted permit |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-08-01 |accessdate=2014-12-19 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809063644/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/7503296.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年12月31日古辛獲外借到[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]，為期1個月，代替另一名因傷返回母會接受治療的借將[[維托·曼諾尼|曼諾尼]]的席位<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/9331207.stm |title=Hull City replace Vito Mannone with Villa's Brad Guzan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-31 |accessdate=2011-03-08 |archive-date=2011-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110102233941/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/9331207.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後獲延長借用至2011年2月底<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/9373574.stm |title=Hull City extend the loan of Villa keeper Brad Guzan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-25 |accessdate=2011-03-08 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815103027/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/9373574.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，文路尼終於傷癒歸隊，古辛亦於上陣11場在借用期滿後返回維拉<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/9409558.stm |title=Hull City sign David Amoo but Brad Guzan exits |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-02-28 |accessdate=2011-03-08 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815203558/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/9409558.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。惟僅一週後，文路尼於復出首場即再次觸傷舊患，古辛以緊急借用形式再次返回侯城效力<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/9417646.stm |title=Hull City re-sign Aston Villa keeper Brad Guzan on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-07 |accessdate=2011-03-08 |archive-date=2011-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110310190914/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/9417646.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年5月23日，[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]宣佈三名主隊成員於六月底約滿後不獲續約，古辛為其中之一<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/18175442 |title=Emile Heskey released by Aston Villa |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-05-23 |accessdate=2014-12-19 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924190854/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/18175442 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年7月16日，原被放棄的古辛獲新任[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]領隊[[保罗·兰伯特|兰伯特]]給與一份新的三年合約，效力至2014/15球季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/18858746 |title=Brad Guzan signs three-year Aston Villa contract |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-07-16 |accessdate=2014-12-19 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924191026/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/18858746 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年7月6日，古辛獲[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]提供一份新的四年合約，令其留隊至2016/17球季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/23210316 |title=Aston Villa goalkeeper Brad Guzan signs new four-year contract |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-07-06 |accessdate=2014-12-19 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924193113/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/23210316 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年7月29日，在阿斯頓維拉降級到[[英冠|英冠]]后，古贊與英超聯賽升班馬[[米德爾斯堡|米德爾斯堡]]達成協議，以免費轉會加入並且簽訂了一份為期兩年的合同<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=https://www.mfc.co.uk/news/boro-agree-deal-to-sign-brad-guzan |title=Boro Agree Deal To Sign Brad Guzan |publisher=''[[米德斯堡|Middlesbrough FC]]'' |date=2016-07-29 |accessdate=2016-07-29 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108132828/https://www.mfc.co.uk/news/boro-agree-deal-to-sign-brad-guzan |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年1月26日，古贊與最近成立的[[MLS|MLS]]球隊[[阿特蘭大聯|阿特蘭大聯]]簽訂了合同，並將在[[2016年至2017年英格蘭足球超級聯賽|2016-17英超聯賽]]結束後返回美國。<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=https://www.atlutd.com/post/2017/01/26/atlanta-united-sign-us-international-brad-guzan |title=Atlanta United Sign U.S. International Brad Guzan |publisher=''[[MLS|MLS]]'' |date=2017-01-26 |accessdate=2017-01-26 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121204800/https://www.atlutd.com/post/2017/01/26/atlanta-united-sign-us-international-brad-guzan |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

